ğŸ”¹ Type Conversion
âœ… Implicit Conversion

Python automatically converts:

5 + 2.0   # 7.0 (float)

âœ… Explicit Conversion

We manually convert:

str(7)
int("10")
float(5)

ğŸ”¹ Important Note (Built-in Functions)

Do NOT overwrite built-in functions:

sum = 10   # âŒ bad practice


Instead use:

sum_
str_
float_

